good deed or healthy act\"] March 4, 2012.\n* [[Roberto Andorno]], [https://www.academia.edu/1488903/Do_our_moral_judgements_need_to_be_guided_by_principles \"Do our moral judgements need to be guided by principles?\"] ''Cambridge Quarterly of Healthcare Ethics'', 2012, 21(4), 457\u201365.\n\n==External links==\n{{Wiktionary}}\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{Commons category|Morality}}\n* [https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/morality-definition/ The Definition of Morality], ''[[Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy]]''\n* [http://moralitylab.bc.edu/publications/ Boston College's Morality Lab]\n* [http://www.chabad.org/search/keyword.asp?kid=1222 Morality and Judaism], [[chabad.org]]\n* [https://www.nytimes.com/2008/01/13/magazine/13Psychology-t.html?pagewanted=print \"The Moral Instinct\"] by [[Steven Pinker]], ''[[The New York Times]]'', 13 January 2008\n\n{{Philosophy topics}}\n{{Ethics}}\n{{Sociobiology}}\n{{Portal bar|Philosophy}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Morality| ]]\n[[Category:Ethics]]\n", "name_user": "Lcscnc", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eSee also", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Morality"}
{"title_page": "Georgios Katsikogiannis", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Georgios Katsikogiannis\n| image =\n| birth_date  = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1988|09|05}}\n| birth_place = [[Athens]], Greece\n| height = {{height|m=1.84|precision=0}}\n| position = [[Defensive midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[Egaleo F.C.|Egaleo]]\n| clubnumber = 88\n| youthyears1=| youthyears2 = \n| youthclubs1 = [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos U-18]] | youthclubs2 =[[Olympiacos U-21]]\n| years1 = 2007\u20132011\n| years2 = 2008\u20132009 \n| years3 = 2010\u20132011\n| years4 = 2011\u20132012\n| years5 = 2012\u20132017\n| years6 = 2017\u20132018\n| years7 = 2019\n| years8 = 2019\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[Olympiacos FC|Olympiacos]] \n| clubs2 = \u2192 [[Levadiakos F.C.|Levadiakos]] (loan) \n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[OFI Crete|OFI]] (loan)\n| clubs4 = [[Doxa Drama F.C.|Doxa Drama]] \n| clubs5 = [[Kallithea F.C.|Kallithea]] \n| clubs6 = [[P.A.O. Aittitos Spata F.C.|Aittitos Spata]]\n| clubs7 = [[Ionikos F.C.|Ionikos]]\n| clubs8 = [[Egaleo F.C.|Egaelo]]\n| caps1 = 8 \n| goals1 = 0 \n| caps2 = 18 \n| goals2 = 0 \n| caps3 = 23\n| goals3 = 0\n| caps4 =  6\n| goals4 = 0\n| caps5 = 123\n| goals5 = 4\n| caps6 = 2\n| goals6 = 0\n| caps7 = 0\n| goals7 = 0\n| caps8 = 0\n| goals8 = 0\n| nationalyears1=\n| nationalteam1=\n| nationalcaps1= | nationalgoals1 = \n| pcupdate = 18:22, 9 December 2018 (UTC)\n| ntupdate = 20:12, March 2008 (CET)\n}}\n\n'''Georgios Katsikogiannis ''' ({{lang-el|\u0393\u03b5\u03ce\u03c1\u03b3\u03b9\u03bf\u03c2 \u039a\u03b1\u03c4\u03c3\u03b9\u03ba\u03bf\u03b3\u03b9\u03ac\u03bd\u03bd\u03b7\u03c2}}, born 5 September 1988) is a Greek professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[defensive midfielder]] for [[Football League (Greece)|Football League]] club [[Egaleo F.C.|Egaleo]].\n\n== Career ==\nBorn in [[Athens]], Katsikogiannis signed his first professional contract with [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] at the start of the 2007/08 season. He made his debut with Olympiacos F.C on 8 December 2007.\n\nIn September 2008, [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos]] expanded his contract for 4 more years and loaned him to [[Levadiakos F.C.|Levadiakos]] for 2 years. After only one-year spell with [[Levadiakos F.C.|Levadiakos]], Olympiacos terminated the loan and brought Katsikogiannis back to the squad for the 2009\u20132010 season.\n\nAs of February 2010,he is on loan to OFI Crete until the end of the season.\n\n== Honours ==\n[[Greek Super Cup|Hellenic Super Cup]]: 2007\n\nGreek [[Super League]]: 2008\n\n[[Greek Cup]]: 2008\n\n== External links ==\n* {{Soccerway}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20120112013431/http://www.onsports.gr/onstats/soccer/player/563-Katsikogiannis-Giorgos Profile] at Onsports.gr\n\n{{Egaleo F.C. squad}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2011}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Katsikogiannis}}\n[[Category:1988 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Greek footballers]]\n[[Category:Olympiacos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Levadiakos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:OFI Crete F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Doxa Drama F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Kallithea F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Superleague Greece players]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Georgios Katsikogiannis\n| image =\n| birth_date  = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|1988|09|05}}\n| birth_place = [[Athens]], Greece\n| height = {{height|m=1.84|precision=0}}\n| position = [[Defensive midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[Egaleo F.C.|Egaleo]]\n| clubnumber = 88\n| youthyears1=| youthyears2 = \n| youthclubs1 = [[Olympiacos F.C.|Olympiacos U-18]] | youthclubs2 =[[Olympiacos U-21]]\n| years1 = 2007\u20132011\n| years2 = 2008\u20132009 \n| years3 = 2010\u20132011\n| years4 = 2011\u20132012\n| years5 = 2012\u20132017\n| years6 = 2017\u20132018\n| years7 = 2019\n| years8 = 2019\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[Olympiacos FC|Olympiacos]] \n| clubs2 = \u2192 [[Levadiakos F.C.|Levadiakos]] (loan) \n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[OFI Crete|OFI]] (loan)\n| clubs4 = [