 [[Paniliakos]], [[Kallithea FC|Kallithea]], [[PAOK FC|PAOK]], [[Panathinaikos FC|Panathinaikos]] and [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Guardian.co.uk |title=Stats Centre: Athanasios Tsigas Facts |url=http://guardian.touch-line.com/StatsCentre.asp?CTID=31&CPID=76&TEID=679&PLID=180666&pStr=Player |accessdate=2008-12-21 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326154510/http://guardian.touch-line.com/StatsCentre.asp?CTID=31&CPID=76&TEID=679&PLID=180666&pStr=Player |archivedate=26 March 2012 |df=dmy }}</ref> He was the first [[Striker (association football)|striker]] that Larissa signed in for [[Super League Greece 2008-09|2008-2009 season]]. On early August 2009, [[Panthrakikos]] expressed their interest on signing Tsigas but he was finally transferred to B' Ethniki Club Kerkyra, with which he climbed to the Superleague.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{Soccerway}}\n\n{{use dmy dates|date= July 2013}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tsigkas, Thanasis}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Alexandroupoli]]\n[[Category:Greek footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Paniliakos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Kallithea F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Panathinaikos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:PAOK FC players]]\n[[Category:Atromitos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:AE Larissa FC players]]\n[[Category:PAE Kerkyra players]]\n[[Category:A.O. Glyfada players]]\n\n\n{{Greece-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|name = Thanasis Tsigas\n|image    =\n|fullname = Athanasios Tsigas\n| height = {{convert|1.86|m|ftin|0|abbr=on}}\n|birth_date = {{Birth date and age|df=y|1982|9|20}}\n| birth_place = [[Alexandroupoli]], [[Greece]]\n|currentclub  = [[Ionikos F.C.]]\n|clubnumber = 11\n|position = [[Forward (association football)|Striker]]\n|youthyears1=1999\u20132001\n|youthclubs1=[[PAE Thraki]]\n| years1 = 2001\u20132004 | clubs1 = [[Paniliakos]]             